{"tid":1589594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［兄弟爬山］去咗日本名古屋.京都揮旗文宣","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:47:36.000Z","uid":18225,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"147a2bae20afa1816a5e3b3b5beaaf3682bf161d","tid":1589594,"uid":18225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"早前有巴打去咗富士山插光復旗<br />\n礙於我唔係行山撚<br />\n所以去咗名古屋立山黑部<br />\n<br />\n除咗喺2400米左右嘅大觀峰揮旗<br />\n亦都喺立山部唔同地方做嗰啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmiQcus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmiQcus.jpg&h=6e27e398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydKvWWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydKvWWb.jpg&h=579ed513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Bn9s2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Bn9s2S.jpg&h=f34e5284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑部峽谷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvy41od.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjvy41od.jpg&h=605fc8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑部水壩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPuTagV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPuTagV.jpg&h=57bb11cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VssEQgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVssEQgV.jpg&h=841f394a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKD8JBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKD8JBW.jpg&h=1e276caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沿途都有日本人、台灣人同外國人<br />\n知我做緊乜<br />\n我都有同佢哋傾計＆做文宣<br />\n當然有手信送畀佢哋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zh2xqQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzh2xqQn.jpg&h=3c26c602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後幾日落咗京都<br />\n去各大寺廟同香港祈願<br />\n因為尊重禮儀 <br />\n所有揮旗只在寺廟外進行<br />\n<br />\n伏見稻荷大社<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u5ZQh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u5ZQh2.jpg&h=45cc445e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyY1jbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyY1jbs.jpg&h=25e8b077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHYQcwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHYQcwu.jpg&h=767e8c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祈願板都好多同路嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n清水寺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybOMviE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybOMviE.jpg&h=4ae9e508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJF7eLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJF7eLu.jpg&h=e93a6315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二年坂三年坂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MTiTUMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMTiTUMb.jpg&h=f57c9830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伊勢神宮内宮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKWqLSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKWqLSz.jpg&h=9d51f0a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇到外國人都會同佢哋文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APZvWZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPZvWZR.jpg&h=ebee1d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近來文宣的確少咗<br />\n希望大家唔好氣餒<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，<br />\n時代革命！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r26RGrW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr26RGrW.gif&h=765ee048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b42a3739b4af6adf82f322f001c3bcd47693f38","tid":1589594,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"「整合」10月1日 分區/一區 優劣勢分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589523</a>"},{"pid":"1e9bd86ceb8d354683556595af5fc56200395514","tid":1589594,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"好感動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝手足<br />\n<br />\n[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94e971481468dcd24a2792e1a28f8b65297d70ea","tid":1589594,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"3ba795f4dcdcd46724a45d3fa98f0268f2edc933","tid":1589594,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"【 9.28 + 10.1 】連發宣傳<br />\n<br />\n五年前的9月28日，催淚彈劃破夏愨道的半空，開展一場劍指真普選的佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，真普選雖仍遙遙無期，而警察比以前更黑、更暴力、更不受監管。但是，香港人履行了在當日佔領結束時許下的承諾 －「人民誓將歸來」。五年後的香港人，以更團結、更鏗鏘、更堅毅的姿態再次站到政權的面前，對抗警暴，爭取雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n9月28日，作為一個我們都記得；我們都認為是重要的日子 － 雨傘運動五周年，我們希望和大家一同回到金鐘，在集會當中沉澱、思考。<br />\n<br />\n同時，縱然當前要舉辦一個合法的遊行是會被多番刁難，而部份手足亦已經視不反對通知書為廢紙，但我們仍入紙希望可以舉辦10.1遊行，盡力讓當日能夠有一個讓所有香港人都能夠參與的大遊行，因此約定大家，十月一日，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【 9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明 】集會<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n【 10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8Dkz2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8Dkz2M.jpg&h=c7d62bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9jQCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9jQCv.jpg&h=769335de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqy41Ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqy41Ka.jpg&h=a6dbaf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJQZQCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJQZQCw.jpg&h=ba39fbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBnxrpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBnxrpS.jpg&h=5d06ca10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32d651ccd53a2844541f46d7e2f13ea60a55551f","tid":1589594,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c6697c06984f1915d855ce7fe006972f0d5a0a","tid":1589594,"uid":195193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af4433f2d5ec716aba9e1fb0127ca64d49b0e24","tid":1589594,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:40:16.000Z","msg":"咁正既post 冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6417027a445688d6a9731a212ee80ff15fbb87a1","tid":1589594,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f704ef424fd4a73782217f63743d3265b8bd751","tid":1589594,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d131d6628c8de1053a3226f77f9d894b7522308a","tid":1589594,"uid":4282